HashMap<String, String> map = new HashMap<>();
map.put("key1", "value1");
map.put("key2", "value2");
map.put("key3", "value3");

Iterator<String> iterator = map.keySet().iterator();
Enumeration<String> enumeration = Collections.enumeration(iterator);

while (enumeration.hasMoreElements()) {
    String key = enumeration.nextElement();
    System.out.println(key);
}
```
This code will print out the keys of the HashMap: key1, key2, key3.

